docs {
  Preset Q&A Management — 6 APIs.
  All requests require the Business-Segment header (Trade | Non-Trade | Key_Accounts).
  Business Segment is server-derived from the header. Customer Segment (CP/CLP/IHB) is optional in request body.
}
